T02D2893:243a-3: tshogs kyi 'khor lo zhes bya ba /
T02D2893:243a-4: gos sngon can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2893:243a-5: gdug pa 'dul byed rdo rje can //
T02D2893:243a-6: de la rtag tu phyag 'tshal te //
T02D2893:243a-7: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs bya'i phyir //
T02D2893:243a-8: tshogs kyi cho ga bshad par bya //
T02D2893:243a-9: gnas khang bden zhing nyams dga' bar //
T02D2893:243a-10: phyag dar chag chag byas nas ni //
T02D2893:243b-0: dkyil @243b 'khor yang ni rab bzhengs la //
T02D2893:243b-1: yang na mandal sngon por bya //
T02D2893:243b-2: gdugs dang ba dan la sogs dbul //
T02D2893:243b-3: rdo rje can gyi rten rnams dgram //
T02D2893:243b-4: mchod pa lnga dang ldan par bya //
T02D2893:243b-5: gtor tshogs rnams kyang bzang du bsham //
T02D2893:243b-6: bdag nyid yi dam lhar ni bskyed //
T02D2893:243b-7: mig gnyis dag tu nyi zla bsgom //
T02D2893:243b-8: de steng h'um ni bsam par bya //
T02D2893:243b-9: phyogs rnams kun tu bltas pas bsreg / de nas gnas ni bsrung bya'i phyir /
T02D2893:243b-10: aom sumbta ni sumbha h'um h'um phat /
T02D2893:243b-11: shar gyi phyogs su rab 'phros pas //
T02D2893:243b-12: rdo rje rigs kyi khro bo ste //
T02D2893:243b-13: sku mdog dkar la 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02D2893:243b-14: phyag na mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs //
T02D2893:243b-15: dpag tu med pas gang bar bskyed //
T02D2893:243b-16: aom grihna grihna h'um h'um phat /
T02D2893:243b-17: rin chen rigs kyi khro bo ste //
T02D2893:243b-18: sku mdog ser la 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02D2893:243b-19: phyag na mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs //
T02D2893:243b-20: dpag tu med pas gang bar bskyed //
T02D2893:243b-21: aom grihn'a pa ya grihn'a pa ya h'um h'um phat /
T02D2893:243b-22: padma rigs kyi khro bo ste //
T02D2893:243b-23: sku mdog dmar la 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02D2893:243b-24: phyag na mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs //
T02D2893:243b-25: dpag tu med pas gang bar bskyed //
T02D2893:243b-26: aom a'a na ya ho bha ga w'an bidy'a r'a dza h'um h'um phat /
T02D2893:243b-27: las kyi rigs kyi khro bo ste //
T02D2893:243b-28: sku mdog sngo la 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
T02D2893:243b-29: phyag na mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs //
T02D2893:243b-30: dpag tu med pas gang bar bskyed //
T02D2893:243b-31: phyogs gsum spros pa shes par bya //
T02D2893:243b-32: rdo rje gur dang ra ba gsum //
T02D2893:243b-33: de la me dpung 'bar ba bskyed //
T02D2893:243b-34: de nas mgron rnams spyan drangs la //
T02D2893:243b-35: bdun po yongs su dag par bya //
T02D2893:243b-36: de nas gtor ma gtor chog bzhin //
T02D2893:243b-37: rgyas par rab tu dbul bar bya //
T02D2893:243b-38: de nas tshogs la bgegs bskrad la //
T02D2893:243b-39: gtor ma byin gyis brlab pa ni //
T02D2893:243b-40: de nas tshogs bdag bkod pa ni //
T02D2893:243b-41: tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag po ni //
T02D2893:243b-42: bcom ldan rdo rje gos sngon can //
T02D2893:243b-43: tshogs kyi bdag po bzhugs su gsol //
T02D2893:243b-44: dus gsum bla ma rnams dang ni //
T02D2893:243b-45: jo bo dkon mchog gsum po dang //
T02D2893:243b-46: bstan pa srung ba'i chos skyong dang //
T02D2893:243b-47: dpal mgon bdun cu rtsa gnyis sogs //
T02D2893:243b-48: tshogs kyi bdag por bzhugs su gsol //
T02D2893:243b-49: de nas tshogs ni dbul ba ni //
T02D2893:243b-50: dus gsum bla ma rnams dang ni //
T02D2893:243b-51: yi dam lha tshogs 'khor bcas la //
T02D2893:244a-2: thugs rje cher dgongs dngos grub stsol //
T02D2893:244a-3: aa la la ste mchod pa bzhes //
T02D2893:244a-4: lha rnams 'dul phyir gos dkar can //
T02D2893:244a-6: lha srin 'dul phyir gos dmar can //
T02D2893:244a-8: klu rnams 'dul phyir gos sngon can //
T02D2893:244a-10: bla med dkon mchog gsum po la //
T02D2893:244a-11: bstan pa srung ba'i chos skyong la //
T02D2893:244a-12: lhag ma yul bdag rnams la sbyin //
T02D2893:244a-13: de nas tshogs la longs spyod pa //
T02D2893:244a-14: lhag ma 'byung po'i gtor ma gtong //
T02D2893:244a-15: glu dang gar dang bskor ba sogs //
T02D2893:244a-16: mchod pa rnam pa sna tshogs dbul //
T02D2893:244a-17: de nas mjug gi las rnams su //
T02D2893:244a-18: mchod bstod yi ge brgya pas bshags //
T02D2893:244a-19: bzod par gsol zhes gshegs pa ni //
T02D2893:244a-20: gang yang bdag blo gti mug pas //
T02D2893:244a-21: legs spyad 'di la nyes pa gang //
T02D2893:244a-22: de kun mgon pos bzod par mdzod //
T02D2893:244a-23: gtso bo nus pa ma mchis shing //
T02D2893:244a-24: ma tshang ba dad mchog pa //
T02D2893:244a-25: de kun mgon pos bzod par mdzod //
T02D2893:244a-26: h'um khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
T02D2893:244a-27: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
T02D2893:244a-28: nyid kyi yul du gshegs su gsol //
T02D2893:244a-29: nyid kyi yul du gshegs nas kyang //
T02D2893:244a-30: thugs kyis brtse bar slar dgongs la //
T02D2893:244a-31: slar yang byon par mdzad du gsol //
